                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>We’re integrating historically distinct areas of expertise and technology into a unified knowledge platform, improving how we collect, analyze and apply data to generate insights faster to help improve patients’ lives. We call it data convergence.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Convergence is the next step in the digital health revolution. We’re leading the way with a data infrastructure that enables more efficient knowledge sharing and understanding across the entire organization — the ultimate goal: a platform that creates new connections and opportunities to better treat disease.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
